Class PtTlsMessageValueSaslMechanismSelectionBuilderIetf

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ietf.nea.pt.value.PtTlsMessageValueSaslMechanismSelectionBuilderIetf
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TransportMessageValueBuilder, TransmissionObjectBuilder<TransportMessageValue>, PtTlsMessageValueSaslMechanismSelectionBuilder

    public class PtTlsMessageValueSaslMechanismSelectionBuilderIetf
extends Object
implements PtTlsMessageValueSaslMechanismSelectionBuilder
    Builder to build a transport SASL mechanism selection message value compliant to RFC 6876. It evaluates the given values and can be used in a fluent way.
